# Power Apps Projects

This section contains Power Apps solutions developed for business process automation, data collection, workflow management, and reporting.

## Featured Projects

### Charter Comments Management App

#### Overview
Developed a Power Apps Canvas Application integrated with Power BI to allow business users to submit, update, and manage charter comments directly from reporting dashboards.

#### Technologies
- Power Apps
- Dataverse
- Power BI
- Power Automate

#### Features
- User comment submission
- Real-time updates
- Integration with Power BI reports
- Role-based access
- Audit tracking

#### Business Impact
Reduced manual email communication and centralized charter review comments within a single platform.

